name: CUE MAZE
description: My second huge effort. This one has many stairways and lifts for a more 3-D feel. Also, alot of puzzles to figure out. Good for Deathmatch as you can get thru all areas in both directions. Hint- To git the Rocket Launcher you must do a "U"-Turn. Dedicated to Computer Users of Erie so don't forget to look at the auto-map before ending the level.
